Hector_quadrotor_demo (TungNV)

Tutorial:
http://wiki.ros.org/hector_quadrotor/Tutorials

Fix bug while building:
https://answers.ros.org/question/244776/is-it-possible-to-run-the-hector_quadrotor-demos-in-kinetic/

Run simulation:
1. Open Serial port for rplidar:
sudo chmod 666 /dev/ttyUSB0

2. Start rplidar:
roslaunch rplidar_ros rplidar.launch
Check rplidar: roslaunch hector_slam_launch tutorial.launch

3. Open seialport for IMU:
sudo chmod 666 /dev/ttyACM0

4. roslaunch mpu6050_ros mpu6050.launch
Check IMU: rostopic echo /mpu6050

3. Run Gazebo and Rviz:
roslaunch hector_TungNV_demo slam_gazebo.launch


NOTE: 
- When open new terminal, need directory source:
soure devel/setup.bash

- show list USB:
ll /dev/tty*

